  "text": "In patients refractory to steroids, azathioprine, mycophenolate mofetil, cyclophosphamide and rituximab have all been tried in addition to, or instead of, steroid therapy [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . However, data for their efficacy is limited with the relevant literature primarily consisting of case series and case reports.",
